item.title: 3 compiling errors HELP!
item.dc:creator: @xxxxxx_13 xxxxxx 13
item.description:
@xxxxxx_13 wrote:

Orphaned case means you closed the main void early and left a case all by its lonesom. The best thing you can do. especially sense this file is so small. go through and count like i do.

{ //count 1 open bracket

~~!$~@$@$@
#%@!%@#^@^
$^!@$^@!^@$@@!$^@!^!
{ // two open brackets
@#%!%!
#@%!#@%!%
!@#%!@ }//one open bracket now since we closed one...
@#%!@%!#
!@#%!@%
}// closed our last bracket
%#@%!@%
!@#%@!%
}//wait a second...we didnt have any open brackets. Uhoh you messed up. :P

OR you can get notepad++ and just see where the int void main is closed at and if its not the last bracket closed or closed when it should be you should fix that. :D
